text: Harringtonia myia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dillon and Dillon in 1946. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Harringtonia myia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1946
